title: Riot Announces Slate of New Games - Kinda Funny Games Daily 10.16.19
description:
Imran and Gary break down all of the announcements from the League of Legends 10th anniversary livestream and The Outer Worlds Xbox One X enhancements.

Time Stamps - 
00:03:55 - Housekeeping
THIS WEEKEND, Kinda Funny’s taking Toronto! EGLX is Saturday and Sunday! kindafunny.com/events!
Saturday 12:30pm - autograph session
Saturday 7:30pm - Smash Bros Royal Rumble (main stage)
Sunday 11am - The Kinda Funny Panel (main stage)
Extra Life is Saturday 11/2! 24 hours of games for charity! Join us now at kindafunny.com/extralife or watch on the day!
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Black Jack & Mohammed Mohammed
The Roper Report   -
00:06:25 - Here's everything Riot announced for League of Legends' 10 year anniversary (Eurogamer by Imogen Beckhelling)
00:16:50 Best Friend Q - What can Riot Games do differently to separate Project A from the very crowded first-person online shooter scene? If you have played LOL, what unique mechanics could they bring over? - BJ Bernado
00:24:55 - Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2 Delayed By Months (IGN by Matt Purslow)
00:30:22 - The Outer Worlds Will Only Be Enhanced On Xbox One X, Not PS4 Pro (Gamespot by Jordan Ramee)
00:45:45 - Out today
00:55: 24 -  BROOKLINEN
00:57:00 -  MANSCAPED
00:58:15 -  ESCAPE THE INVASION
Reader mail   -
01:01:28 - At what point will we finally have enough different forms for Kanto Pokemon? - Trent from VA
01:04:40 - Squad Up: Lucas (Xbox One) - Qawhi Gon Jinn
01:05:10 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts: Greg and Fran
